headline: Molina (MOH) Q3 Earnings Lag Estimates
summary: Molina (MOH) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -53.65% and +5.28%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: The Cigna Group Declares Quarterly Dividend
summary: The Board of Directors of The Cigna Group (NYSE: CI) today declared a cash dividend of $1.51 per share of its common stock, payable on December 18, 2025 to shareholders of record as of the close of business on December 4, 2025.
